<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.7">
<l>kaḷḷac cakaṭum marutum kalakkaḻi yavutai ceyta</l>
<l>piḷḷai yaracēnī pēyaip piṭittu mulaiyuṇ ṭapiṉṉai</l>
<l>yuḷḷavā ṟoṉṟu maṟiyēṉ oḷiyuṭai veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāy</l>
<l>paḷḷikoḷ pōtitu vākum paramaṉē kāppiṭa vārāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Boy King! You who violently kicked the deceptive cart</l>
<l rend="indent">and marutu [trees] to destroy [them]</l>
<l>Then seized the demoness and drank from [her] breast,</l>
<l>I do not know how [you do this].</l>
<l>You who stands in radiant Veḷḷaṟai!</l>
<l>Supreme One! It is time for bed.</l>
<l>Come so that [I can] fasten a Kāppu!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
